#LINUX Commands were directly used on the cloud servers, Containers cause DevOps runs everything on linux. APIs, Databases and servers everything runs on linux, it offers CLI design, easy remote access and lightweight.

Some Important commands for DevOps:

For Directory Management:
ls -lah  - List files with permissions & sizes
du -sh * - Check folder sizes
df -h    - Disk space usage
stat file.txt - Detailed info about file

File Viewing & Editing:
cat file.txt
less file.txt
head -n 20 file.txt
tail -n 50 file.txt
tail -f app.log

File Editing:
nano file.txt
vi file.txt
